init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you watch your next life play out, you can't help but notice that the person playing your future self is being an idiot.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They also appear to be missing some very important information.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: , and you see them shaking their heads in disgust at the decisions future self is making.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "But you've had some great ones as well."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We have, but we've also been some real dopes ourselves!"

actions.text: You are about to say something to previous self when the screen in front of you turns black and the lights come back on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then you look down and see a big black book, with your name on it.
